# Compiled sidecar binaries — built by apps/cockpit/scripts/build-acp-sidecar.ts
# Large real binaries are NOT committed; the stub placeholder IS committed
# (it is required for `cargo build` Tauri validation without network access).
#
# To replace the stub with the real binary, run:
#   bun run apps/cockpit/scripts/build-acp-sidecar.ts
# The real binary is NOT gitignored by name so CI can cache/upload it as an
# artifact; only uncommitted large binaries are excluded here if needed.
